The,Mondido,Payments,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,online,payments,into,their,websites,and,mobile,applications,Mondido,Payments,is,a,Swedish,online,payment,system,that,accepts,a,variety,of,payment,methods,including,PayPal,MasterPass,invoice,Swish,a,Swedish,e,commerce,payment,system,direct,bank,payments,Visa,MasterCard,and,other,cards,such,as,Amex,and,Dankort,It,can,handle,both,one,time,and,recurring,payments